        "TileImage": "$($repository 9e85c891-9eb7-4f3c-8115-896bf54d979b).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47\r\rWe have tracked the masterminds behind the bioweapon. They were hidden allies of the Sheikh and The Constant and are the originators of the blueprints and designs. They keep the knowledge in their minds, refusing physical copies because they think those are impractical.\r\rYour mission: eliminate the inventors to ensure the bioweapon can never be recreated or deployed again.\r\rGood hunting, 47",
